review_blob: Thanks to Borsodi Brewery (InBew) have appeared in the Hungarian stores recently (named by "Unfiltered"). at first sight its promissing but after tasted its quite thin and aqueos. The foam is beautiful and durable. I dont think so give it any advance apple and coriander flavor, I realy do not understand this rather unnecessary. But overall little bit better then an average product of manufacturing (In Hun). Fortunatelly so far is manufactured in Prague.
